# API Configuration
# The axios instance automatically uses:
# Development: http://localhost:5000/api/v1
# Production: https://prompt-studio-0egh.onrender.com/api/v1
# 
# Base URL includes /api/v1 so endpoints are called directly:
# Example: axios.get('/prompts') → https://prompt-studio-0egh.onrender.com/api/v1/prompts
#
# Next.js automatically sets NODE_ENV:
# - development: when running `npm run dev`
# - production: when running `npm run build` and `npm start`
